Title: 架构图
Describe: 整体架构图、AI provider 适配、MCP/插件扩展架构。重点回答“系统怎样分层，变化点在哪里”。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
整体架构图：从入口到工具执行的六层结构

[Description]
Kode CLI 可以看成六层：

1. **入口和协议层**：CLI、ACP、MCP server。
2. **表现层**：Ink REPL、stdio JSON/stream-json、ACP/MCP 协议输出。
3. **应用编排层**：`ask.ts`、`query.ts`、print session、ACP agent。
4. **服务适配层**：LLM providers、MCP clients、plugins、context/system prompt、auth/telemetry。
5. **核心约束层**：Tool 契约、Permission Engine、message normalization、session/auto-compact。
6. **执行能力层**：Bash/File/Search/Task/MCP/Slash/Skill 等工具。

[UML]
@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
top to bottom direction

package "1 入口和协议层" {
  component "cli.tsx / runCli.tsx" as CLI
  component "acp.ts" as ACP
  component "mcp.ts" as MCPServer
}

package "2 表现层" {
  component "REPL.tsx\nInk TUI" as REPL
  component "printMode.ts\ntext/json/stream-json" as Print
  component "KodeAcpAgent\nJSON-RPC updates" as ACPAgent
}

package "3 应用编排层" {
  component "ask.ts\nprint text helper" as Ask
  component "query.ts\nrecursive agent loop" as Query
  component "ToolUseQueue\nscheduler" as Queue
}

package "4 服务适配层" {
  component "llm.ts\nAnthropic/OpenAI/Responses" as LLM
  component "mcp/client.ts\nexternal servers" as MCPClient
  component "pluginRuntime.ts\nplugins" as Plugins
  component "systemPrompt.ts\ncontext prompt" as Prompt
}

package "5 核心约束层" {
  component "Tool interface" as ToolContract
  component "Permission Engine" as Perm
  component "messages/core.ts" as Msg
  component "autoCompactCore.ts" as Compact
}

package "6 执行能力层" {
  component "BashTool" as Bash
  component "FileRead/Edit/Write" as FS
  component "Grep/Glob/Search" as Search
  component "TaskTool" as Task
  component "MCPTool" as MCPTool
  component "SlashCommandTool/SkillTool" as PromptTools
}

CLI --> REPL
CLI --> Print
ACP --> ACPAgent
MCPServer --> ToolContract
REPL --> Query
Print --> Ask
Print --> Query
ACPAgent --> Query
Ask --> Query
Query --> Queue
Query --> LLM
Query --> Prompt
Query --> Msg
Query --> Compact
Queue --> ToolContract
Queue --> Perm
ToolContract --> Bash
ToolContract --> FS
ToolContract --> Search
ToolContract --> Task
ToolContract --> MCPTool
ToolContract --> PromptTools
MCPClient --> MCPTool
Plugins --> MCPClient
Plugins --> PromptTools
Perm --> ToolContract
@enduml

[Detail]
这个图是整份手册的核心架构图。它揭示三个维护原则：

- **入口层不应复制 agent 内核**：不同协议最终都进入 `query` 或 Tool 契约。
- **服务适配层隔离外部变化**：模型 API、MCP transport、插件 manifest 都在 services 中收敛。
- **核心约束层保护执行能力层**：即使工具实现很强，也必须经过 schema、validate、permission、hooks 和消息归一化。

当你需要定位问题时，先问“它破坏的是哪一层的契约”。例如 stream-json 输出异常通常先看 `printMode.ts` 和消息映射；工具安全绕过风险先看 `checkPermissionsAndCallTool` 与 permission engine；模型调用异常先看 `llm.ts` 的 provider 分支和 adapter。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
AI provider 架构：统一 queryLLM，分支适配不同 API

[Description]
`src/services/ai/llm.ts` 是最大、最复杂的服务文件之一。它把上层 `queryCore` 的“给定 prompt/messages/tools，返回 assistant message”请求适配到不同 provider：

- `queryLLM` 解析模型指针、response state、VCR 记录、prompt caching 包装。
- `queryLLMWithPromptCaching` 根据模型类型选择 Anthropic native 或 OpenAI 兼容路径。
- Anthropic path 会处理 SDK client、工具 schema、cache breakpoint、streaming delta、tool_use JSON delta、cost。
- OpenAI path 会处理 Chat Completions、Responses API、GPT-5 变体、usage/cost、responseId。
- `ModelAdapterFactory` 决定某个模型是否走 Responses API 或 Chat Completions。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction

component "queryCore" as QueryCore
component "queryLLM" as QueryLLM
component "queryLLMWithPromptCaching" as PromptCache
component "queryAnthropicNative" as Anthropic
component "queryOpenAI" as OpenAI
component "ModelAdapterFactory" as Factory
component "ResponsesAPI adapter" as Responses
component "ChatCompletions adapter" as Chat
component "buildAssistantMessageFromUnifiedResponse" as BuildMsg
database "responseStateManager" as ResponseState
database "cost and usage\nnormalization" as Cost

QueryCore --> QueryLLM
QueryLLM --> ResponseState
QueryLLM --> PromptCache
PromptCache --> Anthropic : Anthropic-like model
PromptCache --> OpenAI : OpenAI-compatible model
OpenAI --> Factory
Factory --> Responses
Factory --> Chat
Responses --> BuildMsg
Chat --> BuildMsg
Anthropic --> BuildMsg
BuildMsg --> Cost
Cost --> QueryCore
@enduml

[Detail]
这里的设计目标是让 `queryCore` 不关心 provider 细节。上层只需要 assistant message、tool_use、usage、cost、response id 等统一结果。

风险点也很清楚：

- provider 的 streaming 事件结构不同，tool_use 增量解析容易出错。
- Responses API 和 Chat Completions 的 response id、usage 字段、tool schema 差异会影响 session continuation。
- prompt caching、VCR、retry 和 cost logging 是横切能力，改动时要确认不会只覆盖某一个 provider。

开发面试回答可以强调：**模型适配层的难点不是发 HTTP 请求，而是把多 provider 的消息、工具、流式事件、usage 和错误都归一化成 query runtime 能理解的稳定消息。**

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
扩展架构：MCP、插件、命令和技能怎样接入

[Description]
Kode 同时支持外部 MCP server、项目/用户插件、markdown custom commands 和 skills。它们的共同目标是把外部能力转换成 runtime 可消费的 Tool、Command、Hook 或上下文修改器。

关键文件：

- `src/services/mcp/client.ts`：连接 stdio、SSE、HTTP、WS 类型 server，处理超时和 fallback。
- `src/services/mcp/tools-integration.ts`：列出 MCP tools，命名为 `mcp__server__tool`，包装成 Kode Tool。
- `src/services/plugins/pluginRuntime.ts`：加载 plugin manifest，配置 session plugins。
- `src/services/plugins/customCommands.ts`：解析 markdown frontmatter、宏和文件引用。
- `src/tools/interaction/SlashCommandTool/SlashCommandTool.tsx` 与 `src/tools/ai/SkillTool/SkillTool.tsx`：把命令和技能变成 agent 可用工具。

[UML]
@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "外部配置来源" {
  component ".mcp.json / .mcprc\nproject and global MCP" as MCPConfig
  component ".kode-plugin/plugin.json\nplugin manifest" as PluginManifest
  component "markdown command files" as Markdown
  component "marketplace sources" as Marketplace
}

package "解析和加载" {
  component "mcp/discovery.ts" as Discovery
  component "mcp/client.ts" as Client
  component "pluginRuntime.ts" as Runtime
  component "customCommands.ts" as Commands
  component "skillMarketplace.ts" as SkillsMarket
}

package "运行时能力" {
  component "MCPTool" as MCPTool
  component "SlashCommandTool" as SlashTool
  component "SkillTool" as SkillTool
  component "Hooks" as Hooks
  component "Agents and output styles" as Agents
}

component "query runtime" as Query
component "Permission Engine" as Perm

MCPConfig --> Discovery
Discovery --> Client
Client --> MCPTool
PluginManifest --> Runtime
Marketplace --> SkillsMarket
Runtime --> Commands
Runtime --> Client
Runtime --> Hooks
Runtime --> Agents
Markdown --> Commands
Commands --> SlashTool
Commands --> SkillTool
MCPTool --> Query
SlashTool --> Query
SkillTool --> Query
Query --> Perm
@enduml

[Detail]
扩展系统有两个值得复盘的设计取舍：

- **扩展入口很多，但执行入口收敛**：MCP、Skill、SlashCommand 最终还是 Tool 或 prompt modifier，能被 query 和权限系统观察。
- **配置来源按 scope 合并**：user/project/local/plugin 目录都可能贡献能力，开发时必须明确当前会话的配置来源，避免“本机有效、CI 不可复现”。

面试可追问：如果要新增一种外部工具协议，应该接到哪里？合理答案是先实现 services 层的 discovery/client，再包装成 Tool，而不是让 `queryCore` 直接认识新的协议。

------------------------------------------------------------
